Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:24:35.45,WM,,0,0,0,,masssterchief
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.52,0:00:13.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[Former Mitsuhashi Bank Employee, Ushiroda, Activate]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:22.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,66,200...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:27.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The numbers that I'm dealing with looks like fractions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:29.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Fractions?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.70,0:00:34.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,When I worked at Mitsuhashi Bank, I usually deal with transactions in the hundreds of millions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:39.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You know, we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:42.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhashi is a mega bank after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.72,0:00:46.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[Mitsuhashi Bank Begins Layoffs to Reduce Personnel Expenses Through the Use of AI]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:50.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I used to look at the top of peoples head everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:52.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're the one being bowed down to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.58,0:00:54.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'd expect nothing less from Mitsuhashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:56.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ushiroda-san!\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.27,0:00:57.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:01:00.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Invoices? There's a lot of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.22,0:01:01.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.35,0:01:05.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can go on a trip with only the consumption tax.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.06,0:01:12.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,At this stage, we're short of funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.70,0:01:14.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Eh?\N-Ushiroda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.67,0:01:16.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This are the entertainment expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:17.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,And this are the market research expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.92,0:01:19.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Asai-kun, timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:22.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You used too much money.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:25.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? Did we used all of our funds?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:27.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What should we do? \N-President.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.08,0:01:30.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There is not a single company in the world that has not had a financial crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:32.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Companies who relied on us...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:36.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I've seen thousands of companies that relied on Mitsuhashi Bank,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.22,0:01:39.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,In a way, you can say that it's now a full fledged company.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:41.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're here to make sure that doesn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.30,0:01:43.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes. We're just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:47.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ushiroda-san, what is the solution... \N-Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:48.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll get back to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:50.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ushiroda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:53.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You will do something about this matter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:57.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,When the company is in trouble, is where the President is tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.61,0:02:00.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, President!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:04.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:08.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Where is Ushiroda-san? I want to ask for reimbursement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.97,0:02:11.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shinji, your timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.09,0:02:12.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:14.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm also counting on you, Ushiroda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:20.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?\N-We've asked all the places that we could,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:24.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's hard to get additional funding when our service is not up and running.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:28.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Every year, there's one company that is short on funds before the midterm presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:31.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Everyone, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:34.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Wait, you're being too cold, Inuzuka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:37.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Even rockets have to detach parts to go to space.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:40.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You guys are that parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:44.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,At best, make people think they don't want to be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:55.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:03:59.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Options for where to hold the farewell party.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:03.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I've carefully selected the places, so I can guarantee that the food tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:08.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That was so scary that I'm sleepy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:12.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ushiroda-san, what have you been doing all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:20.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ushiroda-san, you used to work for Mitsuhashi Bank, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:23.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I worked at Mitsuhashi Bank for 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:25.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're already a working adult when I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:26.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The day you were born,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:28.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,the day that you first spoke,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.36,0:04:31.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,and when you first put on your backpack, I worked at Mitsuhashi Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:33.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Can you ask Mitsuhashi Bank for a loan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:36.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You must have a lot of juniors that you took good care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:38.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of them, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:40.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,When are you going to ask them? \N-Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:42.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll get back to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:46.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:48.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,From what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:51.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We... I worked at Mitsuhashi Bank for 30 years, nothing scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,With those 30 years, please save DreCra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:56.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please become a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:57.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree?\N-Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:59.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:02.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:05.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,For this amount of money,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:07.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,it's better to go to a mid-to-small sized bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:10.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? Not Mitsuhashi Bank?\N-Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:13.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I think that there's a need for this kind of service, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:16.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We would be very grateful if you would consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:18.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Can I see your business plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:21.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:30.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:32.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I thought that Ushiroda-san was going to bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.15,0:05:37.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, we don't have it with us right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:39.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:42.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If you take the same stance as us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:47.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, if you take the same stance as Mitsuhashi Bank, you will also go downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:51.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you from Mitsuhashi Bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:56.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I worked at Mitsuhashi Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:06:02.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can understand why you might be reluctant to do so because of your own situation and the risks involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:06.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But, how about trying to be brave?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:09.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The one who will be the hero who saves this bank from it's downfall...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:12.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:21.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:24.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We're very cautious when it comes to financing startups,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:23.62,Upper,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhashi Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:27.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,so ultimately it's up to the higher-ups to decide, but
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:29.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I will actively be pushing for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:32.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Our Boss is really something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:33.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Get back to work, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:35.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:38.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:52.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There was someone like that at my previous job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:54.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The mass produced type, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:59.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ushiroda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:05.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No no no, you're Ushiroda-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:08.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Kimura?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:10.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I didn't notice you at all. \N-What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:12.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm helping with a startup here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:13.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sitting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I thought that you've started a business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:20.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:22.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I couldn't imagine you lowering your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:24.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If you show the top of your head...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:26.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:28.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's so Mitsuhashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:29.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Our job, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:32.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhashi's job is business, but
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:34.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,we're just playing business here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't say that.\N-Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:39.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ushiroda-san.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:45.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:50.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Understood. It's a misunderstanding.\N-Ushiroda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You say that it's a misunderstanding, but that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:55.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey you, say that one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:57.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Wait.\N-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:07:59.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Say that one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:00.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Kumamoto-san has snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:04.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We... Mitsuhashi Bank has it's good points,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:07.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,this company also has it's good points.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to say that one is better than the other...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.95,0:08:09.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ushiroda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:12.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:18.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you firing me? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:20.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Fire!\N-You're not serious, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:23.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Fire!\N-She's serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:25.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Not fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:26.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Fire! \N-Not fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:27.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:28.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Not fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:29.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:31.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:33.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Fire!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:37.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That was the first time that I saw you as a President.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:39.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm full of guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:43.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why? I thought that it was the correct fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:46.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Maybe I don't need right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:51.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're not cut out to be a President.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:56.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If only I didn't lose the rock-paper-scissors...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:08.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:10.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:14.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This kind of thing happens a lot in the world of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.71,0:09:15.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ushiroda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:23.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:29.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you want to build one later?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:37.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We're here.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:38.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:40.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes, I've been really into it lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:46.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:47.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:48.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:50.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is he your father?\N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:52.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's Ushiroda-san from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:54.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We'll build one together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:56.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Build one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:58.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Not one drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:10:00.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I've never heard that word before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:01.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:08.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? I'm going to build a plastic model?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:09.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please choose the one that you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:12.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's been tens of years since I last build one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:14.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's no need to force yourself to build one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:16.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ushiroda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:20.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well... If I'm just taking a look...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:37.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:41.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Hurricane V3.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:44.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Cyclone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:46.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's the new Cyclone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:49.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you like Masked Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:54.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, have you seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.47,0:10:55.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.85,0:11:01.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course I've seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:03.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,On the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:06.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:08.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:14.06,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,They actually existed inside the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:19.83,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I share the same impression. I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:22.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,They understand each other. \NI don't know what they're talking about though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:26.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,In that case, there's only one choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:28.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shin Masked Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:30.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's the hero with the big eyes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:33.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I know him.\N-That is the same as not knowing about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.18,0:11:36.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,"Shin Masked Rider" is a work commemorating the 50th anniversary of Masked Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:41.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,As the catchphrase "Things that change, things that don't change, and things that you don't want to change" suggests,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:45.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,"Shin Masked Rider" is a new image of Masked Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:48.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,created while referring to the original manga and the early TV series.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:49.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see that he is your favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:52.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yassan, he took your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:54.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't feel bad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:59.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ushiroda-kun, you can touch Masked Rider if you build this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:00.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:08.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Open the box!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:10.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That was the start signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:17.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:45.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:14.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:17.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:21.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I feel like the texture is different...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:25.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Extra finish is applied to express the texture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:29.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The eyes is pink, so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:31.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Because it's a Rider, please say that it's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:44.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh? There are two scarfs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:46.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can change it depending on the pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Pose?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:53.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It can move like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:14.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:17.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:20.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This also feels different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:22.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:28.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The texture of the suit is expressed using an electro-discharge machining.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:31.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like hard plastic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:35.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The shape of the wrinkles is also different on both legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:38.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I feel like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:42.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm currently touching Masked Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:47.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right. A plastic model is something you can touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:49.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:51.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:56.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Working under a president who is as young as a daughter must be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:09.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who made the President, who is around my daughter's age, worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:15.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I may have been remodeled by Mitsuhashi Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:20.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's not remodeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:23.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's augmentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:26.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If we're talking about the new movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.35,0:15:30.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:35.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can still be a bad guy or a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:42.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We made tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.03,0:15:44.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, Ao-chan made this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:47.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We also have rice crackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.37,0:15:49.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:04.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:06.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You haven't checked the inventory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:08.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? I did it earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:10.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, you didn't. Let's go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:13.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's go.\N-Yassan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:16.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I already did it.\N-You did it yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:18.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yesterday and today, I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:24.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ushiroda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:34.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Because I got emotional, I'm sorry for saying rude things to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:38.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:42.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see that you can also act like that, President.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.22,0:16:48.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I really dislike the way that you refer to Mitsuhashi Bank as "Us" or "We".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:50.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:52.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:57.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's not because I was slacking off?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:59.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:00.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:04.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:10.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,For someone with your experience to choose us and applied for a job with us
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:13.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,was very encouraging and it made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:20.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But, even if you worked at Mitsuhashi Bank even before I was born,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:23.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,you're now Ushiroda-san of DreCra.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:29.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I would be happy that when you say "Us", you're referring to DreCra.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:36.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:40.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:43.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:46.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:18.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yassan, I was right that I already checked the inventory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:19.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:22.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If you've finished it, we say "Give birth".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.22,0:18:30.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:35.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Even though this is a plastic model,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:39.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,it can move more freely than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:44.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Usshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:49.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The range of motion of life, it should be unlimited.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.22,0:18:52.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Usshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:56.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Usshi sounds great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:00.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:07.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I needed that Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:10.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:15.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Finally today...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:19.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:25.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've graduated from Mitsuhashi Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:39.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to be DreCra's hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:49.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:55.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:13.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Masked Rider, give birth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:17.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I hope that he'll come visit again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:19.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We'll see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:51.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Usshi kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.04,0:20:54.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Usshi punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:39.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[New Business Plan]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:47.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.29,0:21:48.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:51.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to negotiate to get funding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:53.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But, our service is not yet up and running...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:56.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:21:59.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Us, Nokoruna, will be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.54,0:22:03.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.77,0:22:05.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.77,0:22:07.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.\N-I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:11.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.\N-Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:15.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ushiroda-san said that us, Nokoruna, will be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:17.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He said "Us".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.25,0:22:29.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.47,0:22:31.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm Ushiroda of Dream Crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.57,0:22:35.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.55,0:22:40.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.85,0:22:43.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[DreCra, Usshi, Activate]
